This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it proposes a novel method for integrating prior information into a deep learning model. Additionally, it may belong to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category as it uses a 3D U-Net for segmentation. Finally, it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with medical image analysis.
